  Our Locations To date, GEO's operations include the management and/or ownership of 143 correctional, detention and community reentry facilities encompassing approximately 100,000 beds, including idle beds in inventory and projects under development.      U.S. Corrections 74 Facilities 80,625 Beds     International Services 7 Facilities 7,861 Beds     Residential Reentry  50 Facilities 10,425 Beds     Non-Residential Reentry 59 Facilities     Youth Services 12 Residential Facilities 1,267 Beds    











